    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304188</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……
か、勝った……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eh? Did we...win? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>フハハ！　貴様らとの戦い、
楽しかったぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hahaha! Fighting you was of
great enjoyment for me. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よかろう。儂の力を貸そう。
契約のための指輪を示せ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll comply with your request. I'll let you
handle my power. Now ready the Pact Ring. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ゆびわって……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ring? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304844</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>指輪を持たぬというのか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't you possess the desired ring? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304844</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>残念だが、契約の指輪を
持たぬ者とは契約はできぬし、
この力を貸すことは叶わぬ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is a problem. Without the proper
Pact Ring we can't form a contract
to which you can use my powers. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No way... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうしよう……
ね、エト……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What do we do...Eto? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305052</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuru! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305148</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>イフリート……
私と……契約、を……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Efreet... Form...a pact...with... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>契約の指輪は
ここにあります……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Pact Ring is lying right here. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305396</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よかろう、ならば儂と戦え！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Very well, in that case let us fight. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>無理だよ！
こんなボロボロなのに！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's absurd! She's too tired for that! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305556</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大丈夫……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's fine... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305664</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お姉さん、
その指輪、わたしたちに
貸してもらえませんか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Miss, could you please lend that ring to us? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305764</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっか……勝ったんだから
いいよな？　オレらでも</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's right...we won, so it's ok
to form a pact with us, right? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305840</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、問題はなかろう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That is correct, I have no objections. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305948</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_042&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……どうしてあなたたちが、
精霊と契約を……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why do you guys want to form a pact
with the Summon Spirit...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306052</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_043&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔術の暴走をおさめるために
精霊の力が必要なんです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We need the power to stop certain
magic from hurting people. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_044&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>レスター博士も
元気づけなきゃだし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We were told to find both the renowned
Lester and the power of the four elements. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306216</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_045&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>レスター……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Lester...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306328</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_046&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう……彼……
……こんな子どもにまで
迷惑かけて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right... Him...These kids...
He went to this extents... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306408</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_047&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……いいわ、使って</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Ok, you can use this. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_048&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、ありがとうございます！
ほら、&lt;Dio&gt;……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you very much! Here, &lt;Dio&gt;... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306592</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_049&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わかってるって。
サンキュ、おばさん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gotcha! Thanks, ma'am! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306776</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_050&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それを指につけたら、
私の言葉を繰り返して……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right then, wear this ring and repeat
the words I'm about to speak. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306776</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_051&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いいかしら……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Got it? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306776</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_052&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>我、今、火の精に願い奉る</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In this moment, I ask for my wishes
to be heard by the deity of Fire. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_053&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>われ、今、火の精に
ねがいたてまつる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In this moment, I ask for my wishes
to be heard by the deity of Fire. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307064</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_055&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>指輪の盟約のもと、
我に精霊を従わせたまえ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let us engage in a contract, as decreed
by the covenant of this ring. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307168</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_056&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>指輪の盟約のもと、
われに精霊を従わせたまえ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let us engage in a contract, as decreed
by the covenant of this ring. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307380</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_058&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よかろう、指輪の盟約のもと、
貴様らに従属せんことを誓おう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Very well, by the contract held on the ring
I shall lend you my power. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307448</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_059&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大丈夫ですか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Are you ok!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_060&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……どうしよう……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...What should we do? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>34</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>307620</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_030_061&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>とりあえず、
&lt;Klarth&gt;さんのところへ
連れて帰ろうよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's take her to &lt;Klarth&gt;'s place for now. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
